text: Usage usage: wfenable <pattern matching expression for workflow names> ... This command enables one or more workflows. Return Codes Listed below are the different return codes for the wfenable command: Code Description 0 Will be returned if the command was successful. 1 Will be returned if the argument count is incorrect. 2 Will be returned if the user is not found or not logged in. 3 Will be returned if no matching workflow was found.
